(68722, 201854, 0, 1, 'Bridges Of Benton County', '', '2010-04-20 00:00:00', 2010, 19, 1, 5, 'Well last time that I saw you, you had fire in your eyes\nYou said that I was never heaven bound\nBut you were bumpin'' and grindin'' on a million guys\nAnd you had the nerve to spit in my eyes\nGo on and burn burn burn those bridges down\n\nYou love to play the victim and you''ve got it all nailed down\nYou''re the best damn actor there in Rogers town\nWell it works for now but what yah gonna do\nWhen there ain''t no one left to cry for you\n''Cause you burn burn burned those bridges down\n\nYou burn burn burned, burned those bridges down\nYou done burned the whole damn lot down to the ground\nWell even before half of them were built\nYou walked on by like it was milk you spilt\nBut you burn burn burned those bridges down\n\nWell I know you love those train songs and those travelin ones too\nSo honey here''s my turn to lay one down\nThe conductor there he''s a callin'' your name\nYou''ve got a one way ticket and the mark of Cain\n''Cause you burn burn burned those bridges down\n\nYou burn burn burned, burned those bridges down\nYou done burned the whole damn lot down to the ground\nTell Charlie and Jeff that I said hello\nWhen you all meet up on down below\n''Cause you burn burn burned those bridges down\n\nWell there may come a time, when you find the sudden urge\nTo come on down and knock upon my door\nWell you can pound and pound until your knuckles bleed\nBut you''ll never hear another peep from me\n''Cause you burn burn burned this bridge on down\n\nYou burn burn burned, burned this bridge on down\nYou done burned the whole damn thing down to the ground\nAnd you can say you''re sorry, and hey thats swell\nBut I sure reckon you can go to hell\n''Cause you burn burn burned this bridge on down\nYou burn burn burned this bridge on down ', '', 156, '', 'Ty Cooper', 'Ty Cooper', 'Andrew Rogers & Ty Cooper', 'None', '', 1, 1, 0, '2013-12-02 01:05:01', '2015-03-12 14:03:12', 